{
  "__inputs": [
    {
      "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
      "label": "Prometheus",
      "description": "",
      "type": "datasource",
      "pluginId": "prometheus",
      "pluginName": "Prometheus"
    }
  ],
  "__requires": [
    {
      "type": "datasource",
      "id": "prometheus",
      "name": "Prometheus",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    },
    {
      "type": "grafana",
      "id": "grafana",
      "name": "Grafana",
      "version": "9.0.0"
    }
  ],
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "description": "Investigates the correlation between Go SDK local activity duration, WFT heartbeats, and server-side WorkflowTaskTimedOut events. Two mechanisms: timer-queue race (mechanism A) and heartbeat chain timeout (mechanism B, deterministic).",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Server \u2014 WFT Timeout Signal",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 3,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 1
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Two server-side paths produce WFT timeout events.** **Mechanism B** (`temporal_workflow_task_heartbeat_timeout_count_total`) is deterministic: fires inside `RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted` when the LA chain has been running past `history.workflowTaskHeartbeatTimeout` (default 30 min). **Mechanism A** (`temporal_start_to_close_timeout_total`) is a race: the server's per-task timer fires before the SDK's heartbeat RPC lands."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "WFT Heartbeat Chain Timeout Rate (Server) \u2014 Mechanism B",
      "description": "Fires inside RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted when OriginalScheduledTime + WorkflowTaskHeartbeatTimeout has elapsed. This is DETERMINISTIC: every heartbeat attempt after the threshold fires this. Rising rate = LAs running past history.workflowTaskHeartbeatTimeout. Metric: temporal_workflow_task_heartbeat_timeout_count_total",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 0.001
              }
            ]
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "min",
            "max",
            "mean",
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (namespace) (rate(temporal_workflow_task_heartbeat_timeout_count_total{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{namespace}}",
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "WFT Start-to-Close Timeout Rate (Server) \u2014 Mechanism A",
      "description": "Fires from the history timer queue when the per-task start-to-close timer expires before the SDK's RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted RPC lands. Intermittent/race-driven. Metric: temporal_start_to_close_timeout_total{operation=TimerActiveTaskWorkflowTaskTimeout}",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 12
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 0.001
              }
            ]
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "min",
            "max",
            "mean",
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (namespace) (rate(temporal_start_to_close_timeout_total{operation=\"TimerActiveTaskWorkflowTaskTimeout\",namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{namespace}}",
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Stale WFT Response on RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted",
      "description": "SDK's heartbeat RPC arrived AFTER server already timed out the task (mechanism A race loser). Each increment = one heartbeat that was too late. Metric: temporal_stale_mutable_state_total{operation=RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted}",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 12
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 0.001
              }
            ]
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "min",
            "max",
            "mean",
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (namespace) (rate(temporal_stale_mutable_state_total{operation=\"RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted\",namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{namespace}}",
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Go SDK \u2014 WFT Execution Pressure",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 19
      },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 3,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 20
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "When LAs run long, `temporal_workflow_task_execution_latency` clusters just below `WFT_timeout \u00d7 0.8` \u2014 the SDK fires a heartbeat at that threshold and a new WFT starts immediately. A p99 pinned near that value means heartbeats are firing continuously on every WFT."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "WFT Execution Latency pNN by Workflow Type",
      "description": "Time to execute a single WFT iteration. When LAs trigger heartbeats, this will cluster near WFT_timeout \u00d7 0.8 (e.g. 8s for a 10s WFT timeout). Metric: temporal_workflow_task_execution_latency_bucket",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 23
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "min",
            "max",
            "mean",
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile($p, sum by (workflow_type, le) (rate(temporal_workflow_task_execution_latency_bucket{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{workflow_type}}",
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "WFT Execution Failed Rate",
      "description": "Rate of WFTs that failed (NonDeterminismError or WorkflowError). Metric: temporal_workflow_task_execution_failed",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 31
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 0.001
