      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 3,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 39
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "This is the root cause section. Rising LA execution latency is what pushes WFT execution latency up toward the heartbeat threshold. **Note:** Go SDK LA metrics carry `workflow_type` and `activity_type` labels \u2014 no `task_queue`."
      }
    },
